title: You Don't Know My Story
description: Black Positive Image, Inc. presents You Don't Know My Story (Vol. 1). You Don't Know My Story is a campaign geared towards recognizing self prosperity through reflection and appreciation that everyone has a life story worth telling. Story submissions are requested from people throughout the community who want to share their story. These stories help to inspire the community by giving back with their voice.
author: Brittney A. Greene
